361
00:21:44,570 --> 00:21:46,732
Character-oriented mechanics then dramatize

362
00:21:46,732 --> 00:21:48,053
this resource management.

363
00:21:48,941 --> 00:21:52,003
By having most, if not all, mechanics in a game

364
00:21:52,003 --> 00:21:55,226
revolve around characters, we can tell powerful narratives

365
00:21:55,226 --> 00:22:00,289
about expectation and betrayal.

366
00:22:00,289 --> 00:22:02,111
Finally, progression through information

367
00:22:02,111 --> 00:22:04,432
allows players to improve over time

368
00:22:04,432 --> 00:22:06,053
without direct empowerment.

369
00:22:07,213 --> 00:22:10,355
Instead of gaining more resources through spatial expansion

370
00:22:10,355 --> 00:22:13,296
or refining them through technological upgrades,

371
00:22:13,296 --> 00:22:15,537
players effectively become more intelligent

